data.description: As you enter through the front door, imagine yourself relaxing in your spacious living room while reading a book or watching TV. Enjoy cooking in the kitchen w/updated painted cabinets, plenty of space for storage w/a pantry, and quaint built-in glass door hutch. Choose your primary bedroom on the 1st floor w/a full bath nearby or the larger bedroom on the 2nd floor w/new LVP flooring. One more bedroom upstairs can also be used as an office and another full bath is ready for your special touches.  Finish the full basement for extra living space and enjoy the 1st-floor laundry as an extra convenience. Take your dog to run and play at Miller Park and enjoy the pool in the summer. A perfect opportunity to call this place home in a great location just a few blocks from downtown Lancaster.
